    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are fully operational, though you should expect some minor fluid seepage and a rougher idle typical of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It is a solid daily driver that starts every time but will eventually benefit from some minor suspension work and a deep clean.",
