    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts. The body has significant structural rust, particularly along the rocker panels and frame, and the paint is heavily oxidized with several large dents. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips, indicating that major repairs are needed before it can be considered roadworthy. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. It is being sold strictly as-is, and towing is recommended.",
