    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Honestly, I'm a bit sad to see this one go, but it's time for a new home. This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014it looks and smells brand new! It's been my absolute pride and joy, always garage-kept and pampered. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
