    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 1995 Mazda RX-7 FD featuring the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine. This specimen exhibits flawless compression across all rotor faces, with the sequential twin-turbocharging system delivering a seamless transition at 4,500 RPM. The chassis is anchored by factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and four-piston calipers, maintaining its legendary 50:50 weight distribution. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 5-speed manual and a Torsen limited-slip differential, with no evidence of thermal fatigue in the engine bay or synchro wear. Meticulously maintained with original VIN-matching panels and a pristine interior, this is a turn-key example for the rotary purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
