    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-quality example that defines the term 'mint.' This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster with no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the leather is supple with absolutely no wear on the bolsters, and the original factory scent persists. Every electronic feature and button functions as new. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a full binder of service records from authorized specialists. It has recently undergone a comprehensive inspection and fluid service to ensure it is turn-key ready. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks and performs exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
